# Mini Student Management System

A simple ASP.NET WebForms project for managing student records. This is an academic-style application demonstrating basic WebForms concepts.

## Project Overview

This project implements a student management system with user registration, login, and CRUD operations for student records. Data is stored in JSON files for simplicity.

## Features

### 1. User Registration (Register.aspx)
- Users can create an account with Username, Email, and Password
- Duplicate username validation
- Simple error and success messages
- Users stored in `App_Data/users.json`

### 2. User Login (Login.aspx)
- Users can login with Username and Password
- Session management (`Session["username"]`)
- HttpCookie with 30-minute expiration
- Redirects to Students page on successful login

### 3. Student Management (Students.aspx)
- Display all students in a GridView
- Add new students with Name, Surname, and Student Number
- Edit student information (GridView Edit/Update)
- Delete students (GridView Delete)
- Duplicate Student Number validation
- Access control: Requires login to view

### 4. Logout (Logout.aspx)
- Abandons session
- Expires authentication cookie
- Redirects to login page

