## Troubleshooting

### "File not found" error
- Ensure App_Data folder exists
- Check file paths in code (using Server.MapPath)

### GridView not updating
- Verify JSON file is being read correctly
- Check that DataBind() is called after loading data

### Login not working
- Verify users.json has been created with register
- Check username and password are exact match
- Ensure no extra spaces in inputs

### Session expires quickly
- Check Web.config sessionState settings
- Cookie expires after 30 minutes of login
